        </div>

        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6">
                <div class="service-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-car service-icon"></i>
                    <h5>Economy Cars</h5>
                    <p>Affordable and fuel-efficient vehicles perfect for city driving and budget-conscious travelers.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6">
                <div class="service-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-gem service-icon"></i>
                    <h5>Luxury Vehicles</h5>
                    <p>Premium cars with advanced features and superior comfort for special occasions and business trips.</p>
